                            <head><hi rend="italic">Memorandum by the Director of the Office of
                                    Military Assistance in the Department of Defense</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_OGGH1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Olmsted</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the Secretary of
