                            <list type="subject">
                                <head>Subject:</head>
                                <item>Reimbursable Military Assistance Under Section 408(<hi rend="italic">e</hi>) of the <gloss target="#t_MDAA1">MDAA</gloss>, as Amended—Case No. OMA India 7</item>
                            </list>
                            <list>
                                <label>1.</label>
                                <item>Reference is made to your memorandum, subject as above, dated
                                        <pb facs="0612" n="1662" xml:id="pg_1662"/> 13 May 1952,
                                    which forwarded note from the Indian Embassy requesting
                                    procurement of fighter aircraft for the Indian
                                    Government.</item>
                                <label>2.</label>
                                <item>In accordance with oral requests made by your office, the
                                    estimated pricing and availability study made by the Department
                                    of the Air Force on the 54 <gloss target="#t_C1">C</gloss>–119
                                    aircraft requested under this case is forwarded for information
                                    and study.</item>
                            </list>
